      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ἐρήμῳ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " as an assertory statement. But on account of the environment of purely interrogatory clauses, and because the author indicates the result at which he aims only in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Hebrews 3:19",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", it seems more correct, with Luther, Calvin, Beza, Mill, Wetstein, Bleek, de Wette, Tholuck, Alford, Maier, and others, to take the whole clause: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "οὐχὶ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " … ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ἐρήμῳ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", together as a single question, in such wise that ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ὧν κ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "τ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "λ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". forms a prolonged characterization of ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "τοῖς ἁμαρτήσασιν",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
